Maxima had left her com on stand-by to Hydras for the time being, as she 
transformed into a sort of vehicle jet mode with animal features, & shot off in 
the direction of Blackstorm & the others. 

Soon enough catching up with the group just moment before they would land to 
rendezvous with the Decepticons. 

"Let's meet these Decepticons, shall we?" As she zoomed up towards Blackstorm 
& Sideways, & nearly shot passed them. Obviously eager to meet up with the 
Decepticons. 


Wasn't look until she caught their signal & they were right in front of them. 


She dived at them, transformed, then landed before the stranded Decepticons. 

Her crimson optics glowed as a wicked smirk appeared upon her face. Glancing 
over the Decepticons before her. She doubted that they would remember her, 
especially in this form, being to animalistic for even her tastes. 

"Greetings, fellow Decepticons," she started off with a commanding yet warm 
welcoming voice, almost like something the 1st Megatron would say, "I am 
Maxima. Declare yourselves to me."

She awaited for their response.

--part1_12f.2b08636e.2c070df7_boundary
